# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Trading Research Platform — .gitignore
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Research-only platform. No live trading, broker execution,
# or production modification is supported or possible.

# ── Python ──────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
*.eggs/
dist/
build/
wheels/
*.whl
pip-wheel-metadata/
.eggs/

# ── Virtual environments ─────────────────────────────────
venv/
.env/
.venv/
env/
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Python tooling ───────────────────────────────────────
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.hypothesis/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/
.nox/
.ruff_cache/
.pytype/

# ── SQLite / databases ──────────────────────────────────
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# ── Redis ───────────────────────────────────────────────
dump.rdb
appendonly.aof

# ── PHP / Laravel ───────────────────────────────────────
/vendor/
/node_modules/
/storage/
bootstrap/cache/
.phpunit.result.cache
*.cache

# ── Composer ────────────────────────────────────────────
composer.phar
composer.lock

# ── Node.js ─────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm/
.yarn/
.pnp.*
package-lock.json

# ── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/
log/

# ── Cache ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.cache/
*.cache
tmp/
temp/

# ── IDE / Editor ────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.project
.classpath
.settings/

# ── Backup archives ─────────────────────────────────────
backups/
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.bak
*.archive

# ── Temporary datasets ──────────────────────────────────
data/
datasets/
*.csv.gz
*.parquet
*.h5
*.hdf5

# ── AI model caches ─────────────────────────────────────
models/
.model_cache/
huggingface/
*.gguf
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.onnx

# ── Output / generated ──────────────────────────────────
output/
results/
artifacts/

# ── OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db

# ── Git ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.orig
*.patch
